headline: Inflation is still 'under control: Citizens CEO on the Fed

Citizens Financial Group (CFG) chairman and CEO Bruce Van Saun sits down with Julie Hyman to share his outlook on the Fed's interest rate policy and the central bank's inflation target, while also commenting on the K-shaped economy.
